<!-- 01 Context -->
<section id="context" class="cs-section">
  <div class="section-eyebrow"><span>01 Context</span></div>
  <h2 class="section-heading">Background</h2>
  <div class="section-cards">

    <div class="card">
      <span class="card-label">The Energy Market</span>
      <p>In 2022, the consumer energy space was becoming turbulent and customers were suddenly exposed to much higher bills. For this reason, Shell's users wanted more insight, more control, and extra guidance on how to use energy more efficiently at home so they can reduce their bills.</p>
      <span class="card-section-label">My Role</span>
      <p>I joined as one of three Product Designers, working across the full design spectrum, from wireframes and prototyping to user testing and stakeholder workshops. Midway through the project I stepped up as Lead, taking ownership of UX research, UI design, and feature strategy, with a focus on engagement and gamification.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
      <span class="card-label">The Brief</span>
      <p>Create an attractive and easy to use app, that would resonate with consumers and offer them an engaging way to manage their household energy usage, beyond just reviewing their monthly bills.</p>
      <span class="card-section-label">Objectives</span>
