  <div class="pilot-box" style="margin-top: 66px; max-width: 60%;">
    <span class="pilot-box-label">🇩🇪 German Market Pilot</span>
    <p>This project was developed in-house at Shell Energy and piloted in the German market with a group of 100 customers. The app was built fully in German and tested across multiple locations, which required close collaboration with local teams and hands-on involvement in user research and testing.</p>
