  <div class="section-row" style="align-items: flex-start; gap: 40px;">
    <div class="section-col">
      <p class="section-body">A large amount of research went into what the solution should be for the 'energy customer of the future'. This research was conducted by the research and innovation team in Germany prior to my joining the team for this project. Some of the key insights that fed into the product vision are outlined below.</p>
    </div>
