    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="insight-cards insight-cards--row">
    <div class="insight-card">
      <p class="insight-quote">"Consumers have higher expectations from their energy provider - wanting more personalised solutions and simple end-to-end experiences for more engagement."</p>
      <span class="insight-source">— Internal Insight</span>
    </div>
    <div class="insight-card">
      <p class="insight-quote">"Users have gone from more 'passive consumption', to having a growing interest and more active participation in the adoption of new energy solutions."</p>
      <span class="insight-source">— Internal Insight</span>
