      <p class="feature-row-body">Real-time household energy data, both total and appliance-level, to provide transparency, trust, and control.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="feature-row">
      <span class="feature-row-number">🎯</span>
      <h4 class="feature-row-title">Product Recommendations & Try-Before-You-Buy</h4>
